help_text="Please set the time before use the app using 'Set time' button. Do not leave any field blank.\n" \
          "Once you are ready press 'start' button.\n You can pause or resume by pressing the 'Pause' button." \
          "\n To set the time again" \
          "or start a new cycle press 'Reset' button first then start. \n Fo rany technical support please contact me at \n " \
          "gmarahma@uwaterloo.ca. \n or visit \n 'https://github.com/gmashik/Python_project/blob/main/Exam_Timer_App/Readme.md'"